snippet: Two boats collided at the start of the ninth and final stage of the Volvo Ocean Race in Lorient, France.
abstract: Two boats collide in final stage of Volvo Ocean Race in Lorient, France, seriously injuring one woman.
lead_paragraph: Two boats collided at the start of the ninth and final stage of the Volvo Ocean Race in Lorient, France.

headline.main: Crash in French Race Injures Woman
